Title: Lightning PDF Professional 7.0.1317.0
Year: 2012
Platform: Windows All
Language: English

Description:
Lightning PDF Professional - Professional program for working with PDF documents. With it you can view, edit and convert PDF files. Lightning PDF Professional is easy to use, efficient, fast and has lots of useful features.

Operating system: Windows XP SP2/Vista SP1
Processor: Pentium III 1 GHz
Memory: 512 MB
Video: 16-bit, 1280x800
Free space on HDD: 50 MB

Features:
 Creating and editing PDF documents;
 Convert PDF to Word;
 Create new and fully customizable forms PDF;
 Document Management;
 Convert PDF documents into JPG, GIF, TIF, etc.;
 Send PDF via E-mail;
 Edit text - cut, copy, paste, resize text and images;
 Graphic editing tools - Add images, geometric shapes, Bezier curves, and more;
 Add notes, watermarks, comments and stamps;
 Create password protected PDF files to restrict access. Set a password on printing, editing, etc.;
 Compatible with Adobe Acrobat or Acrobat Reader, all programs are Microsoft Office, as well as support for javascript.

